{"fadeType":1,"once":true,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"stopbgm":true,"sequence":[["<size=51>The search for truth<\/size>",1],["<size=51>The longing for the future<\/size>",2],["<size=51>The reflection that is there, but always out of reach<\/size>",3],["<size=51>Our battles with destiny most oft end in much the same way<\/size> ",4],["<size=51>Its outcome, as expected<\/size>",5],["<size=51>What is real? What is false?<\/size>",6],["<size=51>All that remains is a small mystery<\/size>",7],["<size=51>So let the tale be told<\/size>",8],["<size=51>Will you, perhaps, solve the mystery?<\/size>",9]]},{"flashout":{"dur":0.5,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"effects":[{"active":true,"name":"xuniyuzhenshi"}],"sequence":[["",1]],"mode":1,"stopbgm":true,"flashin":{"1":5,"delay":0,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true},"blackBg":true},{"flashout":{"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"say":"Noon - Within the Route Escort Fleet","dir":1,"bgm":"level02","side":2,"bgmDelay":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"effects":[{"active":false,"name":"xuniyuzhenshi"}],"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","flashin":{"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Another commission completed without a hitch!","actor":307060,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Nice breeze, calm waves, nice weather all around. I can't wait to get home and take a nap in the sun!","actor":307060,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","paintingFadeOut":{"side":0,"time":0.5},"say":"……","dir":1,"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","actor":301490},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Something wrong, Kawakaze? You're being awfully quiet.","actor":307060,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Oh, it's nothing... I was just thinking about my sword. It'll surely start rusting if they continue giving us nothing but escort missions.","actor":301490,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"I don't mind getting a break from the action. Plus, it's an important job, and someone's gotta do it.","actor":307060,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Speaking of breaks, you need to start letting up that poker face if you hope to make friends. Come on, let's see a smile!","actor":307060,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Uh, Zuikaku, look ahead...","actor":301490,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"... What the heck is that...?","dir":1,"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"effects":[{"active":true,"name":"miwu_01"}],"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","actor":307060},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"It appears to be fog... but there's more to it than that.","actor":301490,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"My gauges indicate the humidity levels and water temperature in the area are changing rapidly. There also seems to be an island coming into view in the distance.","actor":301490,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"All signs point toward this being a Mirror Sea. Come on, Sirens! Can't you at least once let us return home in peace?","dir":1,"side":0,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":30,"delay":0,"dur":0.15,"number":2,"x":0}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","actor":307060},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Detecting numerous mass-produced Siren vessels heading in our direction.","actor":301490,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Kawakaze, you watch the front. I'll scramble my planes in the meanwhile so we can take out the Sirens!","actor":307060,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_nepu1","nameColor":"#a9f548"}],"mode":2,"fadein":1.5,"id":"HOLOGUANQIA2","fadeOut":1.5}